text: Oshunmare (known as Ochumaré or Oxumaré in Latin America) is an Orisha. Osumare is the spirit of the rainbow, and Osumare also means rainbow in the Yoruba language. == See also == * Aido Wedo ==References== Category:Life- death-rebirth deities Category:Yoruba deities Category:Legendary serpents Category:Brazilian deities Category:Candomblé
title: Oshunmare
